channel.description:
ok i've heard some ways to make a webclient and i know they are ok ones ... but they all start wayy too far into the TUTORIAL ... so i felt like i should make a thread asking how to make one from start to finish .... if u have anything at all i will accept it ;D plz i need ppl to help me with this ....
if this works then u can give urself a gold star ;) lol[br][br][size=1]Posted on: March 30, 2009, 05:45:17 pm[/size][hr]soz bout having u move it all the time ... but i dont get y u got rid of my other thing?????? seriously ???? i did nothing wrong on that one .... but i do need help and i forgot to say that it would be helpful if i had some codes to put on ... not just instructions on how to make it ... cuz i know some stuff already ;D
